class Balloon:
    def __init__(self, size, amount, capacity):
        self.size = size
        self.amount = amount
        self.capacity = capacity
        self.fraction = 0

    def inflate(self):
        if self.fraction == 0:
            self.fraction = 1.0
            self.amount += self.size - self.capacity
            self.capacity = self.size
            return

        # Calculate the new fraction of helium to inflate the balloon
        inflate_amount = max(self.amount - self.size, 0)
        inflate_fraction = inflate_amount / self.capacity
        self.fraction = 1.0 - inflate_fraction
        self.amount += inflate_amount
        self.capacity = inflate_amount * self.size

        self.amount = 0
        self.capacity = 0

    def __str__(self):
